Package: linux-sound-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, pipewire, wireplumber, python3-numpy, python3-scipy
Recommends: easyeffects, pavucontrol
Description: SteelSeries Sonar-like audio mixer for Linux
 Linux Sound Manager is a powerful audio mixing application for Linux that
 provides similar functionality to SteelSeries Sonar on Windows.
 .
 Features:
  * 5 audio channels (Game, Chat, Media, Aux, Microphone)
  * Virtual audio devices using PipeWire
  * Parametric EQ (10 bands per channel)
  * Audio effects (Noise Gate, Compressor, Limiter)
  * Spatial audio with 360-degree simulation
  * Preset management
  * EasyEffects integration
  * pavucontrol compatibility
